    "Add spinach, nuts, or salmon to your next meal to easily hit these goals.": {
      "comment": "A suggestion within the micronutrients focus card, encouraging the user to add certain foods to their diet to meet their nutritional goals.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
