    "It's best to track your measurements on the same day each week, at the same time and under the same circumstances.": {
      "comment": "A description under the \"Weight-in\" toggle, explaining the importance of tracking weights at the same time each week.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il est préférable de suivre vos mesures le même jour chaque semaine, à la même heure et dans les mêmes circonstances."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es ist am besten, Ihre Messungen jede Woche am selben Tag, zur gleichen Zeit und unter den gleichen Umständen zu verfolgen."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "È meglio monitorare le misurazioni lo stesso giorno ogni settimana, alla stessa ora e nelle stesse circostanze."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "É melhor monitorar suas medições no mesmo dia da semana, no mesmo horário e nas mesmas circunstâncias."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Лучше всего отслеживать свои измерения в один и тот же день каждую неделю, в одно и то же время и при одних и тех же обстоятельствах."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
