    "Sync nutrition, activity and body measurement with Apple Health app. Data from Apple Health will help give you more accurate recommendations.": {
      "comment": "A description under the \"Sync with Apple Health\" section, explaining how Apple Health data can be used to provide more accurate health recommendations.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Synchronisez la nutrition, l'activité et les mesures corporelles avec l'application Apple Health. Les données d'Apple Health vous aideront à vous donner des recommandations plus précises."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Synchronisieren Sie Ernährung, Aktivität und Körpermessung mit der Apple Health App. Daten von Apple Health helfen Ihnen dabei, genauere Empfehlungen zu geben."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sincronizza alimentazione, attività e misurazione corporea con l'app Apple Salute. I dati di Apple Health ti aiuteranno a darti consigli più accurati."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sincronize nutrição, atividade e medidas corporais com o aplicativo Apple Health. Os dados do Apple Health ajudarão a fornecer recomendações mais precisas."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Синхронизируйте данные о питании, активности и фигуре с приложением Apple Health. Данные Apple Health помогут дать вам более точные рекомендации."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
